==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Approaching
<hw>Ap*proach"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Hort.)</fld> <def>The act of
ingrafting a sprig or shoot of one tree into another, without cutting it
from the parent stock; -- called, also, <xex>inarching</xex> and
<xex>grafting by approach</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Approachless</ent>⟦br⟧
